  <chunk id="b67b75854801b20d8d89d71adf85199ec70c3daa.c2" text="Results: Based on the flexible purely spatial scan statistic, we propose a flexibly shaped space-time scan statistic for early detection of disease outbreaks. The performance of the proposed spacetime scan statistic is compared with that of the cylindrical scan statistic using benchmark data. In order to compare their performances, we have developed a space-time power distribution by extending the purely spatial bivariate power distribution. Daily syndromic surveillance data in Massachusetts, USA, are used to illustrate the proposed test statistic.">
    <entity charOffset="140-147" id="b67b75854801b20d8d89d71adf85199ec70c3daa.c2.e0" ontology_id="DOID_4" text="disease" type="disease"/>
  </chunk>
  <chunk id="b67b75854801b20d8d89d71adf85199ec70c3daa.c3" text="The flexible space-time scan statistic is well suited for detecting and monitoring disease outbreaks in irregularly shaped areas.">
